n.png","title":"Hunter's lemon chicken rissoles","publishedAt":"2017-03-19T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"12.9 g","fat":"11.3 g","uom":"per 1 portions","carbohydrates":"5.5 g","calories":"739 kJ \/ 176 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large baking tray, baking paper, small bowl , bowl, plastic wrap, large frying pan, refrigerator, stove top","hintsAndTricks":["If you would like a bit of heat, add 1 fresh red chilli, cut into halves and deseeded if preferred, when adding the garlic.","This recipe was contributed by Corrinne Hunter."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","1h","12 portions"]}